	<h1 class="title">这个设计了不起之今日最佳</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/161922/small/161922.jpg?1442322894" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">廖婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-15 07:30:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/22244/medium/22244.jpg?1455457565" alt="" />			
	</div>
